>||</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo fence=\"true\">||</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></semantics></math></span>.</p> <p>Therefore, <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_275\"><math alttext=\"\\left\\lVert A\\right\\rVert=\\max_{v\\not=0}\\frac{\\left\\lVert A\\mathbf{v}\\right% \\rVert}{\\left\\lVert\\mathbf{v}\\right\\rVert}=\\max_{v\\not=0}\\frac{\\left\\lVert A(% \\mathbf{w}\\left\\|\\mathbf{v}\\right\\rVert)\\right\\rVert}{\\left\\lVert\\mathbf{v}% \\right\\rVert}=\\max_{\\mathbf{v}\\not=0}\\frac{||\\mathbf{v}||}{||\\mathbf{v}||}\\|A% \\mathbf{w}\\|.\" class=\"ltx_Math\" display=\"inline\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo><mi>A</mi><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><msub><mi>max</mi><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>\u2260</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><mo>\u2061</mo><mfrac><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>\ud835\udc2f</mi></mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo><mi>\ud835\udc2f</mi><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><msub><mi>max</mi><mrow><mi>v</mi><mo>\u2260</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><mo>\u2061</mo><mfrac><mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo><mi>A</mi><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo>\u2225</mo><mi>\ud835\udc2f</mi><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo><mi>\ud835\udc2f</mi><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow></mfrac></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><msub><mi>max</mi><mrow><mi>\ud835\udc2f</mi><mo>\u2260</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></msub><mo>\u2061</mo><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" maxsize=\"142%\" minsize=\"142%\">||</mo><mi>\ud835\udc2f</mi><mo fence=\"true\" maxsize=\"142%\" minsize=\"142%\">||</mo></mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\" maxsize=\"142%\" minsize=\"142%\">||</mo><mi>\ud835\udc2f</mi><mo fence=\"true\" maxsize=\"142%\" minsize=\"142%\">||</mo></mrow></mfrac><mo>\u2062</mo><mrow><mo>\u2225</mo><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi></mrow><mo>\u2225</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo>.</mo></mrow></semantics></math></span> I don't know how to continue from here on. </p> <p>Also, I 'm reading textbooks where they say : <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_276\"><math alttext=\"\\left\\lVert A\\right\\rVert=\\max_{\\|\\mathbf{w}\\|=1}\\|A\\mathbf{w}\\|\\quad for\\quad% \\mathbf{w}\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n}.\" class=\"ltx_Math\" display=\"inline\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo><mi>A</mi><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mrow><msub><mi>max</mi><mrow><mrow><mo>\u2225</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo>\u2225</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>\u2061</mo><mrow><mo>\u2225</mo><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi></mrow><mo>\u2225</mo></mrow></mrow><mo mathvariant=\"italic\" separator=\"true\">\u2003</mo><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>o</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>r</mi></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo mathvariant=\"italic\" separator=\"true\">\u2003</mo><mrow><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo>\u2208</mo><msup><mi>\u211d</mi><mi>n</mi></msup></mrow></mrow><mo>.</mo></mrow></semantics></math></span></p> <p>My question is shouldn't it be  <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_277\"><math alttext=\"\\left\\lVert A\\right\\rVert=\\max_{\\|\\mathbf{w}\\|=1}\\|A\\mathbf{w}\\|\\quad for\\quad% \\mathbf{w}\\in\\mathbb{R}^{n}\\setminus\\{\\mathbf{0}\\}.\" class=\"ltx_Math\" display=\"inline\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo><mi>A</mi><mo fence=\"true\">\u2225</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mrow><mrow><msub><mi>max</mi><mrow><mrow><mo>\u2225</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo>\u2225</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msub><mo>\u2061</mo><mrow><mo>\u2225</mo><mrow><mi>A</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi></mrow><mo>\u2225</mo></mrow></mrow><mo mathvariant=\"italic\" separator=\"true\">\u2003</mo><mrow><mi>f</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>o</mi><mo>\u2062</mo><mi>r</mi></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo mathvariant=\"italic\" separator=\"true\">\u2003</mo><mrow><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo>\u2208</mo><mrow><msup><mi>\u211d</mi><mi>n</mi></msup><mo>\u2216</mo><mrow><mo stretchy=\"false\">{</mo><mn>\ud835\udfce</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">}</mo></mrow></mrow></mrow></mrow><mo>.</mo></mrow></semantics></math></span></p> <p>Because <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_278\"><math alttext=\"\\mathbf{w}=\\mathbf{0}\" class=\"ltx_Math\" display=\"inline\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>\ud835\udfce</mn></mrow></semantics></math></span> means <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_279\"><math alttext=\"||\\mathbf{w}||=0\" class=\"ltx_Math\" display=\"inline\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">||</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo fence=\"true\">||</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></semantics></math></span> which is ruled out because <span class=\"math-container\" id=\"q_280\"><math alttext=\"||\\mathbf{w}||=1.\" class=\"ltx_Math\" display=\"inline\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mrow><mrow><mo fence=\"true\">||</mo><mi>\ud835\udc30</mi><mo fence=\"true\">||</mo></mrow><mo>=</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>.</mo></mrow></semantics></math></span></p>",
